sub_title: Global Marketer | SaaS | CPG | Product Marketing | Advertising | Innovation | Insights
summary:
Strategic marketer thriving on unlocking business potential through creativity and data. Inspiring leader with strong people focus and track record of driving double-digit brand revenue growth across 20+ markets. Sound business acumen, having held global & regional roles in marketing, innovation, shopper marketing and business analytics over the past 15 years. 

Excellent collaboration skills, natural curiosity with a positive, nothing-is-impossible attitude. Passion for adventure sports, art and travelling as well as constant exploration. 

Specialties: Marketing Strategy, Brand Management, Innovation, Marketing Communications, Digital Marketing, Shopper Marketing, Market Research, Revenue Management
